{"tid":1495042,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭同高官都有英藉，聯合聲明失效我地係咪應該爭取","createTime":"2019-08-22T01:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T02:20:46.000Z","uid":94312,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fea3e77188c1467649d48df7ab8cce6d91f063ba","tid":1495042,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:42:49.000Z","msg":"Sorry新手有d1999同錯觀念既話請細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國因為準備脫歐既影響，經濟衰退，人民差唔多五五分裂<br />\n<br />\n而最影響佢地唔同中共作對既原因，似乎都係當地四大電訊商都正在使用華為的設備建設5G網絡，如果限制華為參與，將會造成數十億英鎊損失，但係華為自己都好傷，如果英國最後比華為參與完全係唔洗問我地，為自己英國國民利益優先好合理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但最近竟然出d中共講聯合聲明失效既核彈，英國好似唔敢出聲咁。如果除左五大訴求事成，達到雙普選之餘，我地200萬手足（主要係80, 90後既bno及00父母既cukc）都爭取左完整英藉，但係留係香港監察政府，政府再搞d咩，就威脅200萬人禁錢走資英國。而對英國既最大甜頭，就係華為可以參與英國5G，同埋果200萬人留係抗爭後既民主香港，英國唔洗一下子接收。我好希望呢個緩衝期我地可以200萬人集資再建港，例如去大10倍既福克蘭，重要既係手足安安全全，好似台灣咁同中共保持距離，唔係拘泥於地域。Asgard is not a place, it&rsquo;s a people.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我講到中共好似輸家咁，但係我地呢200萬人走資英國，對佢2047前起大灣區既政治阻力大減，我都係想表達一下，但應唔應該捨棄其他香港既內地同胞，唔係我話事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我原本200萬手足走既概念係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n[BNO平權] [新手求教]福克蘭群島？香港？帶曬200萬手足？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f344f0388321caae9048f8405811693978b94dd8","tid":1495042,"uid":94312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b44f8d1b9545f838540ae6826dcd1a2eb6bba50","tid":1495042,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:46:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec75561f882a530f85cb3ed8e4a6c7d5964607f0","tid":1495042,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"舊公務員所有福利都係英國留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f31fa381b07cea151f0b1d4430e333c485298a","tid":1495042,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec75561f882a530f85cb3ed8e4a6c7d5964607f0","tid":1495042,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"舊公務員所有福利都係英國留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"唔係公務員，聽講而家係合約制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f469806f9361f4d261285139ee4312275d185411","tid":1495042,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:55:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dHmAvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dHmAvS</a>"},{"pid":"4451a126b357b68e173ca46d76f923a2787fdf59","tid":1495042,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw